A graphic novel A Castle in England documents the lives of families who lived in the Scotland Castle from the Middle Ages to the Eduardian period. Each story is illustrated by a different British artist - Isaac Lenkiewicz, Briony May Smith, William Exley, Becky Palmer and Isabel Greenberg.
